    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# 🗺️ Google Maps Lead Scraper\n\nAn automated n8n workflow that searches for businesses on Google Maps, extracts their contact details, and saves unique leads into a Google Sheet.\n\n## 📋 Requirements\n* **n8n Instance:** Cloud or self-hosted via [n8n.io](https://n8n.io).\n* **Google Cloud API Key:** Needs the \"Places API\" enabled to scrape map data. Get this from the [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/).\n* **Google Workspace Account:** To connect and use Google Sheets.\n\n## ⚙️ Step-by-Step Process\n\n1. **🚀 Start:** The workflow is triggered manually via an n8n Form. It sets initial variables and gets the target location.\n2. **🕵️ Scrape:** Makes API requests to Google Places to find businesses. It paginates through up to 3 pages of results, using \"Wait\" nodes to avoid API rate limits.\n3. **🔀 Merge:** Combines the results from all three scraped pages into one list and fetches detailed lead information.\n4. **💾 Insert:** \n   * Reads your existing Google Sheet.\n   * Compares the data to keep only unique leads (no duplicates).\n   * Filters out leads without phone numbers.\n   * Formats the data and appends the new leads into the Google Sheet.\n5. **🏁 End:** Finishes the process and returns a completed form screen.",
